Easy and fast object relational mapping for Kohana framework.

This ORM is a modified version of the standard Kohana ORM.

To use, create a file: application/classes/database/query/builder/where.php:

>abstract class Database_Query_Builder_Where extends Kohana_Database_Query_Builder_Where {
>
>    public function where_array(array $conditions)
>    {
>        $this->_where = $conditions;
>        
>        return $this;
>    }
>}